    <section name="Configuring Portlets">
<p>
To configure a PHP application into your portlet definition, define an init param 
to hold the PHP start page. For example:    
</p>
<source><![CDATA[        
  <init-param>
      <name>StartPage</name>
      <value>hosts/index.php</value>
    </init-param>
]]></source>           
